    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.1",
          "pli": "“… Āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattati. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, when immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated it leads to the ending of defilements. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.2",
          "pli": "Kathaṃ bhāvito ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato saṃyojanappahānāya saṃvattati … ",
          "en": "And how is immersion due to mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated so as to lead to giving up the fetters, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.3",
          "pli": "anusayasamugghātāya saṃvattati … ",
          "en": "uprooting the underlying tendencies, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.4",
          "pli": "addhānapariññāya saṃvattati … ",
          "en": "completely understanding the course of time, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.5",
          "pli": "āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattati? ",
          "en": "and ending the defilements? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.6",
          "pli": "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā … pe … ",
          "en": "It’s when a mendicant—gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or to an empty hut—sits down cross-legged, with their body straight, and focuses their mindfulness right there. … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.7",
          "pli": "paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmīti sikkhati, paṭinissaggānupassī passasissāmīti sikkhati. ",
          "en": "They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.8",
          "pli": "Evaṃ bhāvito kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi evaṃ bahulīkato saṃyojanappahānāya saṃvattati … pe … ",
          "en": "That’s how immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated so as to lead to giving up the fetters, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.9",
          "pli": "anusayasamugghātāya saṃvattati … pe … ",
          "en": "uprooting the underlying tendencies, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.10",
          "pli": "addhānapariññāya saṃvattati … pe … ",
          "en": "completely understanding the course of time, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.11",
          "pli": "āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattatī”ti. ",
          "en": "and ending the defilements.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.12",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:1.13",
          "pli": "Dutiyo vaggo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:2.1",
          "pli": "Icchānaṅgalaṃ kaṅkheyyaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:2.2",
          "pli": "ānandā apare duve; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:2.3",
          "pli": "Bhikkhū saṃyojanānusayā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:2.4",
          "pli": "addhānaṃ āsavakkhayanti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn54.20:2.5",
          "pli": "Ānāpānasaṃyuttaṃ dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": "The Linked Discourses on Mindfulness of Breathing is the tenth section."
        }
      ],
